title: PMC Notification 2025 - Walk-in interview for 27 Senior Resident Posts
description: The Pune Municipal Corporation (PMC) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 27 Senior Resident Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their MBBS can apply for the PMC Notification 2025 . The interested applicants can attend the walk-in interview.
